  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the lamb shoulder and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the ground cumin, ground coriander, smoked paprika, cayenne pepper, and black pepper. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the yuzu juice, lemon juice, and salt. Stir to combine.",
    "Cover the pot and transfer it to the oven. Bake at 300°F (150°C) for 2 1/2 hours, until the lamb is tender.",
    "Shred the lamb with two forks and return it to the pot.",
    "Stir in the chopped fresh parsley.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
  ],
